eg:\par
Letter Search - letter by letter routine : 0.00006 sec per call\par
Word Searck Mask: 0.0002 sec per call\par
Word Search Meta : 0.05 sec per call\par
Word Search Meta with optimum backtrack: 0.09 sec per call\par
